subsection.p:
First of all your module needs a Makefile.in file. It need not be
         more complicated than the following example:

# $Id$
@make_variables@
VPATH=@srcdir@:@srcdir@/../..:../..
OBJS=
MODULE_LDFLAGS=@LDFLAGS@ @LIBS@

CONFIG_HEADERS=@CONFIG_HEADERS@

@dynamic_module_makefile@
@dependencies@
